      "widgets_values": [
        "IAMCCS SuperNodes - Minimal Startup Guide\n\nRequired:\n- IAMCCS-nodes installed.\n- LTXV model, text encoder/CLIP, Video VAE, Audio VAE.\n- Video combine support and audio duration helpers.\n- MelBand RoFormer model if using vocal-focused lipsync.\n\nFirst test:\n1. Planner: modern pipeline + single generation + melband_vocals_duration_math.\n2. Render: audio+image2video.\n3. VAE: normal_tiled_iamccs.\n4. Use a clear face/mouth image and a simple speech/singing prompt.\n\nNext tests:\n- 2 segments before 3 or loop.\n- Legacy pipeline only if you want to compare the older behavior.\n- low_ram/very_low_ram only when memory requires it.\n\nIf lipsync is missing, check:\n- mouth visibility in the image;\n- Audio Mode;\n- FPS consistency;\n- final audio from Exec VAE audio_passthrough;\n- image_strength too high/low for the shot.\n\nCode by Carmine Cristallo Scalzi AI research (IAMCCS) patreon.com/IAMCCS"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
