      "widgets_values": [
        "IAMCCS Exec Render - Quick Start\n\nThis is the generation node.\n\nGeneration Type:\n- audio+image2video: audio-driven image animation. Use the Planner to choose modern/legacy and single/segments/loop.\n- text+audio2video: audio-driven text-to-video. Single generation only.\n- img2video: image-to-video without input-audio driving.\n- text2video: text-to-video without input-audio driving.\n\nRecommended starting values:\n- width/height: 1280x720 default; LTX may internally round height to 736.\n- steps: 8.\n- cfg: 1.0.\n- image_strength: 0.9 default. Use 1.0 for stronger image fidelity, 0.8 for more motion.\n- image_compression: 33-35.\n- Second Stage: off.\n- Latent Refresh: off/beta.\n\nFor segmented joins:\n- keep Stitch custom + cut first.\n- if the join is visible, try Color Match = luma_only, strength 0.15-0.25.\n- adjust Overlap Frames in the Planner, not here.\n\n\nCode by Carmine Cristallo Scalzi AI research (IAMCCS) patreon.com/IAMCCS"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
    {
      "id": 6039,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        -1807.8233346898767,
        125.16002974685617
      ],
      "size": [
